	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Is it possible to use heat in some way to soften/melt the plastic and remould it into a flat surface, e.g. using a small/flat metal sheet, heating it up somehow, then applying it evenly to the surface of the pad so that the little &quot;centre mound&quot; flattens out?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


